      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ROYALE (7) goes very well over this track and trip including two wins. Recorded a 4 length win (15.88) in a Grade 5 last time at Cannington. With a clean break looks hard to beat. FEDERAL FOCUS (1) missed the frame last time at this track but was in the finish the start prior when fifth (30.31) and goes well this journey. Can turn it around this time. BOSS DELUXE (3) had been in great form, scoring back to wins before copping a check last time and finishing fourth (22.97), beaten 3 lengths in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Key player if finds best. WAVE OF FUN (2) surprised many with a win last start and is in the mix again.",
